The Functional data application module supports the requirement to record:
the structure and classification of products, activities, documents, organizations and people;
the properties of products and activities;
the library identification of classes of product and activity.
individual products, activities, documents, organizations and people, and their structure and classification with respect to libraries of classes of product, activity, document, organization and person;
This is within the scope of the Structure_and_classification application module.
properties of products and activities;
This is within the scope of the Property_and_property_assignment application module.
library identification of classes of product and activity.
This is within the scope of the Library_identification application module.
shape and position of products;
schematic representation of product, activities, documents, organization or employment structure.
This is within the scope of the Functional_data_and_schematic_representation application module.
